   "source": [
    "# ForensicLens AI Backend - Google Colab GPU Setup\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook sets up and runs the ForensicLens AI backend on Google Colab GPU.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Runtime Setup:**\n",
    "1. Runtime → Change runtime type → GPU\n",
    "2. Run all cells in order\n",
    "3. Note the ngrok URL for frontend integration"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Check GPU Availability"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import torch\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"PyTorch version: {torch.__version__}\")\n",
    "print(f\"CUDA available: {torch.cuda.is_available()}\")\n",
    "\n",
    "if torch.cuda.is_available():\n",
    "    print(f\"CUDA version: {torch.version.cuda}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"GPU: {torch.cuda.get_device_name(0)}\")\n",
    "    print(f\"GPU Memory: {torch.cuda.get_device_properties(0).total_memory / 1e9:.2f} GB\")\n",
    "else:\n",
    "    print(\"⚠️ No GPU available! Change runtime to GPU.\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Clone Repository and Install Dependencies"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Clone repository\n",
    "# Replace <YOUR_REPO_URL> with your actual repository URL\n",
    "!git clone <YOUR_REPO_URL> /content/forensiclens_backend\n",
    "\n",
    "# Change to project directory\n",
    "%cd /content/forensiclens_backend\n",
    "\n",
    "# Install dependencies\n",
    "!pip install -q -r requirements.txt\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ Dependencies installed successfully!\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Setup Environment Variables\n",
    "\n",
    "**Important:** Update these values with your actual credentials!"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import os\n",
    "\n",
    "# Application Configuration\n",
    "os.environ['APP_NAME'] = 'ForensicLens AI Backend'\n",
    "os.environ['DEBUG'] = 'False'\n",
    "os.environ['API_PREFIX'] = '/api/v1'\n",
    "\n",
    "# Server\n",
    "os.environ['HOST'] = '0.0.0.0'\n",
    "os.environ['PORT'] = '8000'\n",
    "\n",
    "# CORS - Update with your Next.js frontend URL\n",
    "os.environ['CORS_ORIGINS'] = '*'  # Change to your frontend URL in production\n",
    "\n",
    "# Database - Update with your PostgreSQL connection\n",
    "os.environ['DATABASE_URL'] = 'postgresql://user:password@host:5432/database'\n",
    "\n",
    "# JWT Secret - Generate with: openssl rand -hex 32\n",
    "os.environ['SECRET_KEY'] = 'your-super-secret-jwt-key-change-this'\n",
    "\n",
    "# File Storage\n",
    "os.environ['UPLOAD_DIR'] = 'uploads/original'\n",
    "os.environ['PROCESSED_DIR'] = 'uploads/processed'\n",
    "\n",
    "# AI Configuration\n",
    "os.environ['USE_GPU'] = 'True'\n",
    "os.environ['BATCH_SIZE'] = '4'\n",
    "\n",
    "# ngrok - Get your token from: https://dashboard.ngrok.com/get-started/your-authtoken\n",
    "os.environ['NGROK_AUTH_TOKEN'] = 'your-ngrok-auth-token-here'\n",
    "os.environ['NGROK_ENABLED'] = 'False'  # Will enable manually\n",
    "\n",
    "# Logging\n",
    "os.environ['LOG_LEVEL'] = 'INFO'\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ Environment variables configured!\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Create Upload Directories"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "!mkdir -p uploads/original uploads/processed models\n",
    "print(\"✅ Directories created!\")"
   ]
  },
